					<description><![CDATA[<p>Is your YouTube account set up for advertising success? Find out what you need to do.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/optimize-youtube-ad-campaigns">5 Quick Ways to Optimize Your YouTube Ad Campaigns</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
