<li><a href="#pros-of-youtube">When to use YouTube</a></li>
<li><a href="#pros-of-tiktok">When to use TikTok</a></li>
<li><a href="#how-to-choose-between-tiktok-vs-youtube">How to choose between TikTok vs. YouTube?</a></li>
