					<description><![CDATA[<p>Ready to get your business seen where your audience is binge-watching their favorite shows and movies? Then this complete guide to Hulu advertising is just what you're looking for.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/09/06/hulu-advertising">The Complete, Beginner-Friendly Guide to Hulu Advertising in 2024</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I hate to break it to anyone with a satellite dish hanging off their roof right now, but gone are the days of cable TV.</p>
<p>Now, don&#8217;t get me wrong, I love relaxing on the couch to binge-watch my favorite shows and movies as much as the next person. Luckily, that enriching activity won&#8217;t be out of the picture anytime soon. However, <em>how</em> we do that is what&#8217;s changing. <a href="https://home.admanager.hulu.com/insights/how-small-businesses-can-create-impactful-streaming-tv-ads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">6 out of 10</a> adults in the US now stream content through major streaming service subscription platforms like Hulu, Netflix, Peacock, Max by HBO, Showtime, Disney+, and more. In fact, people are watching twice as many hours of content each day via a streaming service as they do via live television. So, while old-school television might become a blast from the past, streaming is here to stay.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/streaming-tv-stat.jpg" alt="stat that states people watch twice as much content via streaming than they do via tv" width="936" height="357" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-75829" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/streaming-tv-stat.jpg 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/streaming-tv-stat-480x183.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Of course, this transition to on-demand content opens tons of new opportunities for you to advertise your business. With Hulu being the<a href="https://tinuiti.com/blog/ott-over-the-top-ads/hulu-advertising-ott/#:~:text=OTT%20advertising%20is%20advertising%20delivered,streaming%20services%20today%20is%20Hulu." target="_blank" rel="noopener"> top</a> ad-supported streaming platform in the US, it&#8217;s a natural fit for anyone looking to start out in streamed advertising. However, unlike more established online advertising platforms such as Google Ads or Meta Ads, Hulu launched its advertising platform only a few years back in 2020 and it&#8217;s still in beta. So, if you have questions about how to get started with Hulu advertising, that&#8217;s more than understandable‚Äîwhich is why we&#8217;re breaking down everything you need to know to set your Hulu ads up for success!</p>
<div class='et-box et-shadow'>
					<div class='et-box-content'><span style="text-decoration: line-through;"></span></p>
<h3>Table of contents</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#what">What is Hulu advertising?</a></li>
<li><a href="#works">How does Hulu advertising work?</a></li>
<li><a href="#types">Types of Hulu ads</a></li>
<li><a href="#benefits">Benefits of Hulu advertising</a></li>
<li><a href="#start">How to advertise on Hulu</a></li>
<li><a href="#tips">Hulu advertising tips</a></li>
</ul></div></div>
<div id="what"></div>
<h2>What is Hulu advertising?</h2>
<p>Before you get to know Hulu advertising, you‚Äôll want to first be familiar with Hulu as a platform. Hulu is a streaming app that allows its subscribers to watch movies and TV shows on demand. You can stream Hulu on virtually any device, such as mobile phones, gaming consoles, tablets, or smart or connected TVs (CTV).</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketing-channels-ott-advertising-infographic.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - ott advertising chart" width="829" height="533" class="aligncenter wp-image-73296 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketing-channels-ott-advertising-infographic.jpg 829w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketing-channels-ott-advertising-infographic-480x309.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 829px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Hulu ads are a type of <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/09/09/what-ott-advertising" target="_blank" rel="noopener">over-the-top (OTT) advertising</a> that includes non-skippable video ads that are shown before, during, and after streamed content on Hulu.</p>
<div id="works"></div>
<h2>How does Hulu advertising work?</h2>
<p>All Hulu ads are purchased via the Hulu Ad Manager‚Äîwhich, again, is still in beta. However, it can be helpful to know that Hulu is owned by Disney, so you may have heard of businesses buying Hulu ads through Disney Ad Manager. Disney Ad Manager and Hulu Ad Manager are one and the same. You can sign up for the <a href="https://home.admanager.hulu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hulu Ad Manager</a> beta and either choose to pay for ads that solely show on Hulu, or also show ads on other Disney-owned streaming platforms, like Disney+, as well.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-disney-ad-manager.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - disney ad manager definition" width="758" height="336" class="aligncenter wp-image-75772 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-disney-ad-manager.jpg 758w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-disney-ad-manager-480x213.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 758px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>We&#8217;ll walk through how to get started with Hulu advertising in a bit.</p>
<h3>Who can advertise on Hulu?</h3>
<p>Since Hulu is only currently available in the US, any US-based business can advertise on Hulu.</p>
<h3>How much does Hulu advertising cost?</h3>
<p>Hulu requires a minimum spend of $500 per campaign. Of course, how much you put behind your total Hulu advertising costs is dependent on what‚Äôs feasible for your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/marketing-budget/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marketing budget</a> and objectives. That said, it‚Äôs been found that your typical Hulu video ad costs anywhere from <a href="https://saaspartners.io/how-much-does-it-cost-to-advertise-on-hulu/#:~:text=The%20cost%20of%20advertising%20on,Hulu%20is%20a%20great%20option.">$10 to $30</a> per one thousand impressions.</p>
<div id="types"></div>
<h2>Types of Hulu ads</h2>
<p>All Hulu ads are video-based and between 15 to 30 seconds long. However, there are a few different types of Hulu ad placements advertisers can choose from that serve different purposes. Some, like the branded slate and cover story brand placement ads, are more suited for enterprises or entertainment corporations that partner with Hulu and Disney.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-enterprise-ads.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - enterprise level ads from hulu" width="900" height="433" class="aligncenter wp-image-75780 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-enterprise-ads.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-enterprise-ads-480x231.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Others can be a fit for small businesses starting out with Hulu advertising, like:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Ad selector ads:</strong> With ad selector ads, you provide two to three ads, and this gives your viewers the option to choose which ad from your business they‚Äôd prefer to view.</li>
<li><strong>Binge ads: </strong>Binge ads are similar to¬†typical Hulu video ads, but instead of showing before or after a streaming selection, they‚Äôre shown throughout a binge session of three or more episodes streamed in a row.</li>
</ul>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-ad-selector-binge-ads.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - ad selector and binge ad examples" width="900" height="637" class="aligncenter wp-image-75785 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-ad-selector-binge-ads.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-ad-selector-binge-ads-480x340.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Interactive ads:</strong> These Hulu ads could be a video or more of a still-frame image, but the differentiator here is that they prompt users to click off to <a href="https://marketing.localiq.com/WSLiQContentDLHowToMakeGreatLandingPages.html?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_LandingPages_HowToMakeGreatLandingPagesGuide_Download" target="_blank" rel="noopener">your business‚Äôs landing page</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-interactive-ads.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - interactive ad example leading to a business landing page " width="519" height="603" class="aligncenter wp-image-75774 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-interactive-ads.jpg 519w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-interactive-ads-480x558.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 519px, 100vw" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Pause ads: </strong>Pause ads¬†overlay the pause screen of a show or movie (pro tip: pause ads can be a great way to implement<a href="https://localiq.com/blog/qr-code-marketing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> QR code marketing</a>).</li>
</ul>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-pause-ad.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - pause ad example" width="537" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-75784 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-pause-ad.jpg 537w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-pause-ad-480x536.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 537px, 100vw" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Video commercial:</strong> These are your typical Hulu video ad shown before, during, or after a streamed program.</li>
</ul>
<p>You can find a complete list of all available <a href="https://hulu.disneyadvertising.com/ad-products/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hulu ad products</a> here.</p>
<div class='et-box et-shadow'>
					<div class='et-box-content'><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="üö®" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Free guide &gt;&gt; <a href="https://marketing.wordstream.com/WSContentDLWebBlogInContentTextLinkAllStarPlaybook.html?cid=Web_Blog_InContent_TextLink_AllStarPlaybook_Download">All-Start Online Advertising Playbook</a></div></div>
<div id="benefits"></div>
<h2>Benefits of Hulu advertising</h2>
<p>With a full understanding of all that Hulu advertising entails, you can start to think about whether it‚Äôs a good fit for your business‚Äôs <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/01/18/best-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marketing strategy</a>. Consider these statistics:</p>
<ul>
<li>With <a href="https://home.admanager.hulu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">112 million</a> monthly US viewers, Hulu is the <a href="https://tinuiti.com/blog/ott-over-the-top-ads/hulu-advertising-ott/#:~:text=OTT%20advertising%20is%20advertising%20delivered,streaming%20services%20today%20is%20Hulu." target="_blank" rel="noopener">leading</a> ad-supported TV streaming service.</li>
<li>Hulu‚Äôs ad selector feature has proven to be <a href="https://designloud.com/7-tips-advertising-hulu-streaming-services/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">150%</a> more effective than regular TV ads at developing recall and 24% better at creating viewer <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2016/01/26/intent-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">purchasing intent</a>.</li>
<li>Hulu ads are nearly <a href="https://designloud.com/7-tips-advertising-hulu-streaming-services/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">200%</a> more effective in creating top-of-mind awareness when compared to other ad formats.</li>
</ul>
<p>On top of this, it‚Äôs important to reiterate that Hulu‚Äôs unique ad selector feature allows your audience to <em>choose to view your ad</em>‚Äîresulting in a viewership that&#8217;s eager to learn more about your business. Plus, its ability to allow advertisers to target via a combination of program genre, audience interest, and zip code is something other emerging platforms, like <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/05/23/tiktok-ads-targeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok Ads</a>, don‚Äôt necessarily have yet.</p>
<div id="start"></div>
<h2>How to get started with Hulu advertising</h2>
<p>Here are the steps to get started with Hulu advertising:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Navigate</strong> to https://home.admanager.hulu.com/ and <strong>sign up</strong> for Hulu Ad Manager (this would be considered your RSVP to the Hulu Ad Manager beta program).</li>
<li><strong>Follow the prompts</strong> to set up a new campaign schedule and budget.</li>
</ol>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-scheduling.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - scheduling a campaign example" width="742" height="423" class="aligncenter wp-image-75777 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-scheduling.jpg 742w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-scheduling-480x274.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 742px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.searchenginejournal.com/hulu-launches-beta-for-self-serve-advertising-platform/374772/#close" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<ol start="3">
<li><strong>Select</strong> who you want your ads to show to with the prompts for audience targeting. This is where you determine settings like locations, audience interests, program genres, and more.</li>
<li><strong>Upload</strong> a video ad for review. (If you don‚Äôt have the resources to create your own video ad, you could check out <a href="https://home.admanager.hulu.com/creative-directory/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hulu‚Äôs list of recommended creative providers</a>, or see how <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/marketing-services" target="_blank" rel="noopener">our solutions</a> can help!)</li>
<li>Once you upload your ad for review, you‚Äôll be prompted to <strong>add a credit card</strong> for payment.</li>
<li>Congratulations, your business is officially using Hulu advertising! Now, you can hop back into Ads Manager regularly to<strong> view your campaign performance</strong> and measure your success.</li>
</ol>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-dashboard.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - ad manager dashboard" width="481" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-75783 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-dashboard.jpg 481w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-dashboard-241x300.jpg 241w" sizes="(max-width: 481px) 100vw, 481px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.searchenginejournal.com/hulu-launches-beta-for-self-serve-advertising-platform/374772/#close" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<div id="tips"></div>
<h2>3 quick Hulu advertising tips</h2>
<p>Now that you‚Äôre ready to take advantage of all that this<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/06/26/marketing-channels" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> marketing channel</a> has to offer, here are some Hulu advertising tips to keep in mind.</p>
<h3>1. Follow video creative best practices</h3>
<p>To increase your chances of <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/06/23/google-ads-disapprovals" target="_blank" rel="noopener">getting your ads approved</a>, you‚Äôll of course want to abide by all the technical requirements and specifications Hulu outlines for its ads.</p>
<p>For example, all Hulu ads should be between 15 and 30 seconds long and come in the form of a .mov or .mp4 file. Additionally, your ad file size can‚Äôt exceed 10 GB.</p>
<p>You can find a complete outline of <a href="https://home.admanager.hulu.com/tech-specs-for-video-ads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">technical specs from Hulu here</a>, but aside from what‚Äôs required, there are some recommended creative best practices for your Hulu ads as well:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Get your point across quickly. </strong>Since you won‚Äôt have a lot of time to convey your message to your audience, you‚Äôll want to ensure that the main points of your ads shine through in both the imagery and the script.</li>
<li><strong>Keep your branding consistent.</strong> You‚Äôll want your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-make-your-business-stand-out/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">business to stand out</a> as your audience is watching your Hulu advertising. For example, including your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/small-business-logo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">small business logo</a> and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/07/12/color-psychology-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">brand colors </a>across all your video frames can help reinforce your brand. In fact, Hulu found that the top-performing 15-second ads were also <a href="https://home.admanager.hulu.com/insights/how-small-businesses-can-create-impactful-streaming-tv-ads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">12 times</a> more likely to include branding throughout the ad.</li>
</ul>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-branding-statistics.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - stats on branding" width="936" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-75790 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-branding-statistics.jpg 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-branding-statistics-480x308.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://home.admanager.hulu.com/insights/how-small-businesses-can-create-impactful-streaming-tv-ads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Data source</a></em></p>
<h3>2. Regularly measure your Hulu ad performance</h3>
<p>With at least $500 on the line, you don‚Äôt want to just set and forget your Hulu ads. Luckily, Hulu makes it easy to track performance right from within the Hulu Ad Manager. Simply log in and, on the ad manager homepage, you‚Äôll get a breakdown of all your campaigns.</p>
<p>To help keep track of your success, be sure to <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/06/15/marketing-objectives" target="_blank" rel="noopener">set measurable goals </a>to track your campaigns against. You‚Äôll likely want to benchmark your progress along the way. You could even refer to <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/05/15/google-ads-benchmarks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">industry benchmarks</a> of other top ad platforms to see how your Hulu ads compare to channels like Google Ads.</p>
<div class='et-box et-shadow'>
					<div class='et-box-content'>Use our<a href="https://marketing.localiq.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsiteGoogleAdsBenchmarks2023.html?cid=Web_WS_incontent_guide_2023benchmarks_Download&amp;utm_source=wordstream&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=incontent_links" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> latest Google Ads benchmarks report</a> to see how your Hulu ad costs compare to average PPC costs in your industry.</div></div>
<h3>3. Frequently upload fresh ads</h3>
<p>We can all probably recall a commercial we‚Äôve sadly seen far too many times. Hulu subscribers tend to stream on the platform in large chunks‚Äîwhich means it&#8217;s more likely that your audience could see your ad multiple times. The last thing you want to do is overtire your audience with a repetitive ad!</p>
<p>Avoid this by refreshing and reuploading your ads regularly. However, it&#8217;s a best practice to let any sort of marketing campaign run for at least a month before you judge its efficacy. So, instead of stressing to refresh your ads weekly, try revisiting them monthly or quarterly. That way, you can make data-backed decisions on how you might want to tweak them.</p>
<p>If you&#8217;re short on ideas to keep your ads fresh, try leaning into seasonal themes. For example, you could use a <a href="https://localiq.com/resources/2023-marketing-calendar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marketing calendar</a> (like the one below from our friends at LocaliQ) to pre-plan your Hulu ad video content. That way, you&#8217;re always prepared to change up your ad as needed.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-ad-planning-calendar.jpg" alt="hulu advertising - example calendar for video content planning" width="736" height="559" class="aligncenter wp-image-75791 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-ad-planning-calendar.jpg 736w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hulu-advertising-ad-planning-calendar-480x365.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 736px, 100vw" /></p>
<h2>Get started with Hulu advertising ASAP</h2>
<p>The best part about Hulu advertising? It&#8217;s still in beta, so odds are, your competitors aren‚Äôt yet on the platform. This provides an opportunity for your brand to stand out and reach your audience in a more intimate way as they‚Äôre streaming content. If you get started with Hulu advertising and still have questions, <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/marketing-services">we‚Äôve got you covered</a>.</p>
<p>To recap, here is a summary of the steps to get started with Hulu advertising:</p>
<ol>
<li>Navigate to https://home.admanager.hulu.com/ and sign up for Hulu ad manager.</li>
<li>Follow the prompts to set up a new campaign schedule and budget.</li>
<li>Select your audience targeting.</li>
<li>Upload a video ad for review.</li>
<li>Add a credit card for payment.</li>
<li>Congratulations, your business is officially using Hulu advertising!</li>
</ol>
